1. *Martine*, šta se dešava? (Martin, what's happening?)
2. Ne mogu danas da izađem sa tobom, *martine*. (I can't go out with you today, Martin.)
3. Gde si bio sinoć, *martine*? (Where were you last night, Martin?)
4. *Martine*, daj mi taj olovku. (Martin, give me that pencil.)
5. *Martine*, pošalji mi mejl sa informacijama. (Martin, send me an email with the information.)
6. *Martine*, treba mi tvoja pomoć oko ovog zadatka. (Martin, I need your help with this task.)
7. Ovaj stolac je *martinov*. (This chair is Martin's.)
8. *Martinu* je drago što si došao na žurku. (Martin is glad that you came to the party.)
9. Naše omiljeno mesto za izlazak je *martinova* kafeterija. (Our favorite place to hang out is Martin's café.)
10. *Martinom* upravlja kompanija koja se bavi prodajom automobila. (Martin manages a company that sells cars.)